title: Spare hours...
author: Brown, John
snippet: It is hard to say whether he loves boys or girls most, — those delightful little men on their ponies in the hunting-fields, those charming little  Lady Adas flirting at the juvenile ball; or Tom the butcher's boy, on the slide ; or ragged little Emly pulling  the go-cart freighted with Elizarann and her doll.
